Gold Price in Hong Kong Down 
The gold price in Hong Kong dropped 12 HK dollars to close at 2,698 HK
dollars a tael on Friday, according to Po Sang Bank, one of the major
gold dealers in Hong Kong.
The gold price is equivalent to 292.26 U.S. dollars a troy ounce, down
1.55 U.S. dollars from the previous close at Friday's exchange rate of
one U.S. dollar to 7.7490 HK dollars.
